front.title: •It's A Hit!
front.gametext: USED: Cancel a Force drain at a site related to a system you control.  LOST: Cancel Counter Assault, It's Worse, Elis Helrot, Tallon Roll, Limited Resources or Scanning Crew. OR Use 3 Force to search your Lost Pile and take one non-unique starfighter into hand.
front.lore: Red Leader fired the first shot in the Death Star trench, causing massive internal damage. The spectacular near-miss inspired Red Squadron to double their efforts.

pulls: One non-unique starfighter from Lost Pile
cancels: A Force drain at a site related to a system you control
